title: Getting Started
text: refinebioc package collection functions can used refine Bioconductor objects. package designed used conjunction BiocFileCache package, provides way cache Bioconductor objects disk. refinebioc package provides functions refine cached objects, filtering, normalizing, transforming data.

title: Getting Started
text: experiment_listing function can used list available experiments. get feel data, can look first rows data frame. experiments variable contains data frame. Standard dplyr functions can used filter sort data frame. rb_get_experiment function loads experiment data memory. refine.bio website API, data loaded, prepares data asynchronously, function wait data ready, often taking minutes. interrupt function running. expts variable contains list SummarizedExperiment objects. view sample information, use colData function.

title: Getting Started
Getting Started
text: experiment_listing function can used list available experiments. get feel data, can look first rows data frame. experiments variable contains data frame. Standard dplyr functions can used filter sort data frame.
